{"title":"Orcish ring mail/zh-CN","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Orcish_ring_mail/zh-CN","type":"markdown","data":"**NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！**  \n[了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki](/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN \"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\")\n\n**[English](/wiki/Orcish_ring_mail \"Orcish ring mail\")** • [中文（中国大陆）‎]()\n\n| \\[   兽人锁环甲   [![Orcish ring mail.png](/images/e/e2/Orcish_ring_mail.png)](/wiki/File:Orcish_ring_mail.png) |                                                                                                                 |\n| ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| 外观                                                                                                         | 粗糙锁环甲                                                                                                           |\n|                                                                                                            |                                                                                                                 |\n| 装备槽位                                                                                                       | [铠甲](/wiki/%E9%93%A0%E7%94%B2 \"铠甲\")                                                                             |\n| AC                                                                                                         | [2](/index.php?title=%E6%8A%A4%E7%94%B2%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"护甲等级 (page does not exist)\") |\n| 特殊效果                                                                                                       | - [MC1](/index.php?title=%E9%94%80%E9%AD%94\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"销魔 (page does not exist)\")                 |\n|                                                                                                            |                                                                                                                 |\n| 基础价                                                                                                        | 80 [zm](/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81 \"金币\")                                                                          |\n| 重量                                                                                                         | [250](/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"重量 (page does not exist)\")                   |\n| 材料                                                                                                         | [铁](/index.php?title=%E9%93%81\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"铁 (page does not exist)\")                               |\n\n**兽人锁环甲**（orcish ring mail）是[NetHack](/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")中的一种[铠甲](/wiki/%E9%93%A0%E7%94%B2 \"铠甲\")类[防具](/wiki/%E9%98%B2%E5%85%B7 \"防具\")，它由[铁](/index.php?title=%E9%93%81\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"铁 (page does not exist)\")制成，未[鉴定](/index.php?title=%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"鉴定 (page does not exist)\")时外观为**粗糙锁环甲**（crude ring mail）。\n\n[ ]\n\n## Contents\n\n- [1 生成](#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90)\n\n- [2 描述](#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0)\n\n- [3 策略](#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5)\n\n- [4 历史](#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2)\n\n- [5 Variants](#Variants)\n\n  - [5.1 UnNetHack](#UnNetHack)\n  - [5.2 dNethack](#dNethack)\n  - [5.3 EvilHack](#EvilHack)\n\n- [6 引用及注释](#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A)\n\n## 生成\n\n[兽人](/index.php?title=%E5%85%BD%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%88%E8%B5%B7%E5%A7%8B%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%EF%BC%89\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"兽人（起始种族） (page does not exist)\")族角色在游戏开始时即鉴定兽人锁环甲[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1)。兽人[野蛮人](/index.php?title=%E9%87%8E%E8%9B%AE%E4%BA%BA\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"野蛮人 (page does not exist)\")在游戏开始时会获得一件兽人锁环甲[\\[2\\]](#cite_note-2)[\\[3\\]](#cite_note-3)。\n\n## 描述\n\n兽人锁环甲的基础[AC](/index.php?title=AC/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"AC/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")加成为2，并能提供[MC](/index.php?title=MC/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"MC/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")1。\n\n## 策略\n\n兽人锁环甲的重量与普通[锁环甲](/wiki/%E9%94%81%E7%8E%AF%E7%94%B2 \"锁环甲\")相同，但是防护性能更低，兽人野蛮人应当尽快把它换成更好的防具。对于大多数角色，即使是[皮甲](/wiki/%E7%9A%AE%E7%94%B2 \"皮甲\")都比兽人锁环甲强，因为皮甲的基础AC加成和它一样，但更轻，而且不阻碍[施法](/index.php?title=%E6%96%BD%E6%B3%95\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"施法 (page does not exist)\")。\n\n## 历史\n\n兽人锁环甲最初于[NetHack 3.0.0](/wiki/NetHack_3.0.0 \"NetHack 3.0.0\")加入游戏。\n\n## Variants\n\n**此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。**  \n您可以帮助我们[**翻译此页面**](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Orcish_ring_mail/zh-CN\\&action=edit)，但**请勿使用机器翻译**。\n\nSome variants may give orcs (including orcish player characters) an AC bonus for wearing orcish ring mail.\n\n### UnNetHack\n\nIn [UnNetHack](/wiki/UnNetHack \"UnNetHack\"), orcish ring mail grants +1 AC to orcish monsters that wear them, including orcish characters.\n\n### dNethack\n\nIn [dNetHack](/wiki/DNetHack \"DNetHack\") and [notdNetHack](/wiki/NotdNetHack \"NotdNetHack\"), orcish chain mail grants 1 AC, 1 [DR](/wiki/DR \"DR\") and MC1 when worn, and its weight is reduced to 125 aum (half of its weight in vanilla *NetHack*).\n\n### EvilHack\n\nIn [EvilHack](/wiki/EvilHack \"EvilHack\"), orcish ring mail grants +1 AC to orcish monsters that wear them, including orcish characters.\n\nOrcish chain mail can be created at a [forge](/wiki/Forge_\\(dungeon_feature\\) \"Forge (dungeon feature)\") by combining an [orcish helm](/wiki/Orcish_helm \"Orcish helm\") and an [orcish shield](/wiki/Orcish_shield \"Orcish shield\").\n\nAll of this information also applies to [Hack'EM](/wiki/Hack%27EM \"Hack'EM\").\n\n## 引用及注释\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [src/u\\_init.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 860](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/u_init.c#L860)\n2. [↑](#cite_ref-2) [src/u\\_init.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 46](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/u_init.c#L46)\n3. [↑](#cite_ref-3) [src/u\\_init.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 220](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/u_init.c#L220)\n\n[![此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。](/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png)](/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version \"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\")\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Orcish ring mail/zh-CN - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Orcish_ring_mail/zh-CN\",\"wgTitle\":\"Orcish ring mail/zh-CN\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":168618,\"wgRevisionId\":168618,\"wgArticleId\":39794,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"待翻译页面\",\"Nethack-367 articles\",\"Body armor/zh-CN\",\"Orcish items/zh-CN\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Orcish_ring_mail/zh-CN\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":39794,\"wgRequestId\":\"7dae0ad3200481849ec3b814\",\"wgCSPNonce\":false,\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[],\"wgWikiEditorEnabledModules\":[],\"wgCategoryTreePageCategoryOp