olspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-darkgray\">[</span> &#8194; 兽人锁环甲 &#8194; <a href=\"/wiki/File:Orcish_ring_mail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Orcish ring mail.png\" src=\"/images/e/e2/Orcish_ring_mail.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td>粗糙锁环甲\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>装备槽位\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%93%A0%E7%94%B2\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"铠甲\">铠甲</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>AC\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%8A%A4%E7%94%B2%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"护甲等级 (page does not exist)\">2</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>特殊效果\n</th>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%94%80%E9%AD%94&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"销魔 (page does not exist)\">MC1</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>80 <a href=\"/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"金币\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">250</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>材料\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>兽人锁环甲</b>（orcish ring mail）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%93%A0%E7%94%B2\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"铠甲\">铠甲</a>类<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%98%B2%E5%85%B7\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"防具\">防具</a>，它由<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>制成，未<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"鉴定 (page does not exist)\">鉴定</a>时外观为<b>粗糙锁环甲</b>（crude ring mail）。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">描述</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#UnNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">UnNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#dNethack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">dNethack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#EvilHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">EvilHack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%85%BD%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%88%E8%B5%B7%E5%A7%8B%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%EF%BC%89&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"兽人（起始种族） (page does not exist)\">兽人</a>族角色在游戏开始时即鉴定兽人锁环甲<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。兽人<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8E%E8%9B%AE%E4%BA%BA&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"野蛮人 (page does not exist)\">野蛮人</a>在游戏开始时会获得一件兽人锁环甲<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"描述\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\">描述</span></h2>\n<p>兽人锁环甲的基础<a href=\"/index.php?title=AC/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"AC/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">AC</a>加成为2，并能提供<a href=\"/index.php?title=MC/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"MC/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">MC</a>1。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>兽人锁环甲的重量与普通<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%94%81%E7%8E%AF%E7%94%B2\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"锁环甲\">锁环甲</a>相同，但是防护性能更低，兽人野蛮人应当尽快把它换成更好的防具。对于大多数角色，即使是<a href=\"/wiki/%E7%9A%AE%E7%94%B2\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"皮甲\">皮甲</a>都比兽人锁环甲强，因为皮甲的基础AC加成和它一样，但更轻，而且不阻碍<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%96%BD%E6%B3%95&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"施法 (page does not exist)\">施法</a>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>兽人锁环甲最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.0.0\" title=\"NetHack 3.0.0\">NetHack 3.0.0</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Orcish_ring_mail/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<p>Some variants may give orcs (including orcish player characters) an AC bonus for wearing orcish ring mail.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"UnNetHack\">UnNetHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/UnNetHack\" title=\"UnNetHack\">UnNetHack</a>, orcish ring mail grants +1 AC to orcish monsters that wear them, including orcish characters.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"dNethack\">dNethack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/DNetHack\" title=\"DNetHack\">dNetHack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/NotdNetHack\" title=\"NotdNetHack\">notdNetHack</a>, orcish chain mail grants 1 AC, 1 <a href=\"/wiki/DR\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"DR\">DR</a> and MC1 when worn, and its weight is reduced to 125 aum (half of its weight in vanilla <i>NetHack</i>).\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/EvilHack\" title=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</a>, orcish ring mail grants +1 AC to orcish monsters that wear them, including orcish characters.\n</p><p>Orcish chain mail can be created at a <a href=\"/wiki/Forge_(dungeon_feature)\" title=\"Forge (dungeon feature)\">forge</a> by combining an <a href=\"/wiki/Orcish_helm\" title=\"Orcish helm\">orcish helm</a> and an <a href=\"/wiki/Orcish_shield\" title=\"Orcish shield\">orcish shield</a>.\n</p><p>All of this information also applies to <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/u_init.c#L860\">src/u_init.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 860</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/u_init.c#L46\">src/u_init.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 46</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/u_init.c#L220\">src/u_init.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 220</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926185544\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.035 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.046 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 536/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2410/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5165/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 728/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 5/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1196/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   33.141      1 -total\n 23.08%    7.649      1 Template:Armor/zh-CN\n 21.66%    7.177      3 Template:Refsrc\n 20.38%    6.753      1 Template:Languages\n 15.96%    5.290      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n 14.71%    4.874      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 12.27%    4.066      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\n 11.12%    3.686      1 Template:Autotile\n  9.17%    3.039      3 Template:Refsrc/link\n  7.31%    2.423      1 Template:Top_icon\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:39794-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926185544 and revision id 168618\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t