 both;\"></div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgPageParseReport\":{\"limitreport\":{\"cputime\":\"0.035\",\"walltime\":\"0.046\",\"ppvisitednodes\":{\"value\":536,\"limit\":1000000},\"ppgeneratednodes\":{\"value\":2410,\"limit\":1000000},\"postexpandincludesize\":{\"value\":5165,\"limit\":2097152},\"templateargumentsize\":{\"value\":728,\"limit\":2097152},\"expansiondepth\":{\"value\":10,\"limit\":40},\"expensivefunctioncount\":{\"value\":5,\"limit\":100},\"unstrip-depth\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":20},\"unstrip-size\":{\"value\":1196,\"limit\":5000000},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%   33.141      1 -total\",\" 23.08%    7.649      1 Template:Armor/zh-CN\",\" 21.66%    7.177      3 Template:Refsrc\",\" 20.38%    6.753      1 Template:Languages\",\" 15.96%    5.290      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\",\" 14.71%    4.874      5 Template:Languages/Lang\",\" 12.27%    4.066      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\",\" 11.12%    3.686      1 Template:Autotile\",\"  9.17%    3.039      3 Template:Refsrc/link\",\"  7.31%    2.423      1 Template:Top_icon\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240926185544\",\"ttl\":604800,\"transientcontent\":false}}});mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":89});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{needhelp/zh-CN}}\n{{languages}}\n{{armor/zh-CN\n  |color=black\n  |name=兽人锁环甲\n  |appearance=粗糙锁环甲\n  |slot=铠甲\n  |ac=2\n  |special=<ul><li>[[销魔|MC1]]</li></ul>\n  |cost=80\n  |weight=250\n  |material=铁\n}}\n'''兽人锁环甲'''（orcish ring mail）是{{cnlink|NetHack}}中的一种[[铠甲]]类[[防具]]，它由[[铁]]制成，未[[鉴定]]时外观为'''粗糙锁环甲'''（crude ring mail）。\n\n== 生成 ==\n[[兽人（起始种族）|兽人]]族角色在游戏开始时即鉴定兽人锁环甲{{refsrc|src/u_init.c|860|nethack=3.6.7}}。兽人[[野蛮人]]在游戏开始时会获得一件兽人锁环甲{{refsrc|src/u_init.c|46|nethack=3.6.7}}{{refsrc|src/u_init.c|220|nethack=3.6.7}}。\n\n== 描述 ==\n兽人锁环甲的基础{{cnlink|AC}}加成为2，并能提供{{cnlink|MC}}1。\n\n== 策略 ==\n兽人锁环甲的重量与普通[[锁环甲]]相同，但是防护性能更低，兽人野蛮人应当尽快把它换成更好的防具。对于大多数角色，即使是[[皮甲]]都比兽人锁环甲强，因为皮甲的基础AC加成和它一样，但更轻，而且不阻碍[[施法]]。\n\n== 历史 ==\n兽人锁环甲最初于[[NetHack 3.0.0]]加入游戏。\n\n==Variants==\n{{translation/zh-CN|n}}\nSome variants may give orcs (including orcish player characters) an AC bonus for wearing orcish ring mail.\n\n===UnNetHack===\nIn [[UnNetHack]], orcish ring mail grants +1 AC to orcish monsters that wear them, including orcish characters.\n\n===dNethack===\nIn [[dNetHack]] and [[notdNetHack]], orcish chain mail grants 1 AC, 1 [[DR]] and MC1 when worn, and its weight is reduced to 125 aum (half of its weight in vanilla ''NetHack'').\n\n===EvilHack===\nIn [[EvilHack]], orcish ring mail grants +1 AC to orcish monsters that wear them, including orcish characters.\n\nOrcish chain mail can be created at a [[Forge (dungeon feature)|forge]] by combining an [[orcish helm]] and an [[orcish shield]].\n\nAll of this information also applies to [[Hack'EM]].\n\n== 引用及注释 ==\n<references/>\n{{nethack-367/zh-CN}}\n[[Category:Body armor/zh-CN|SHOURENSUOHUANJIA]]\n[[Category:Orcish items/zh-CN|SUOHUANJIA]]"}